      "item": {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "3f6560ae89766908",
        "text": "Before the legitimacy validity reaches its actual goal - as a legitimacy belief in the social vertical from the bottom to the top - it is always already there in a developed form (even a coercive rule is always legitimate in this sense before the \"actual\" legitimacy process even begins). This is another peculiar additional opportunity that arises for its actors already in the first phases of the formation of power: the internal construction of that consciousness that offers motives of docility beyond habit and interest. Here, too, a power potency accumulates as if by itself."
      },
      "date": 1665863581941
